  🎩 Safar Aashray — Refugee Housing Design

  The Big Idea

  "Safar Aashray" (Safar Shelter) — a module within the existing platform connecting displaced persons
  with housing through a 3-sided marketplace: Hosts, Refugees, and Funding Organizations
  (NGOs/governments/CSR).

